  <brief_title>Comparison of Gated Blood-pool SPECT and Echocardiogram for Ventricular Function</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Gated Blood-pool SPECT Using CZT Camera and Echocardiogram for Ventricular Ejection Fraction Estimation</official_title>
  <sponsors>
